name: virtuoso-opensource
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "7.2.7" %}

package:
  name: virtuoso-opensource
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/openlink/virtuoso-opensource/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 5e3f68fe43030dfcec461211ae4401620009b872f70abad061a90c0b9cefb2f0

build:
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [win]

requirements:
  # > from README.md
  #   tool      min     max
  # #########  ######  ######
  # autoconf   2.57    2.69
  # automake   1.9     1.16.1
  # bison      2.3     3.5.1
  # flex       2.5.33  2.6.4
  # gawk       3.1.1   5.0.1
  # gperf      3.0.1   3.1
  # libtool    1.5     2.4.6
  # m4         1.4.1   1.4.18
  # make       3.79.1  4.2.1
  # openssl    0.9.8e  3.0.x

  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - autoconf 2.*  # [unix]
    - automake 1.*  # [unix]
    - libtool 2.*  # [unix]
    - flex 2.*  # [unix]
    - bison <3.6  # [unix]
    - gperf 3.*  # [unix]
    - gawk <5.1  # [unix]
    - m4 1.*  # [unix]
    - make 4.*  # [unix]
  host:
    - openssl
  run:
    - openssl


test:
  commands:
    # virtuoso-t, isql, isqlw, virt_mail, virtuoso-sample-t, inifile
    - isql --help

about:
  home: https://virtuoso.openlinksw.com
  license: GPL-2.0-only
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: COPYING
  summary: |
    Virtuoso is a high-performance and scalable Multi-Model RDBMS, Data
    Integration Middleware, Linked Data Deployment, and HTTP Application Server
    Platform
  doc_url: http://vos.openlinksw.com/owiki/wiki/VOS
  dev_url: https://github.com/openlink/virtuoso-opensource

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bollwyvl
